Class Customer

java.lang.Object
bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model.Customer
public class Customer extends Object
Represents a customer (passenger) in the Flight Booking System. A customer can make one or more bookings.

    • addBooking

      public void addBooking(Booking booking) throws FlightBookingSystemException
      Adds a booking to the customer. A customer must not have two bookings for the same flight.
      Parameters:
      booking - the booking to add
      Throws:
      FlightBookingSystemException - if booking for the same flight already exists

    • cancelBookingForFlight

      public void cancelBookingForFlight(Flight flight) throws FlightBookingSystemException
      Cancels (removes) the booking for the given flight from this customer.
      Parameters:
      flight - the flight to cancel booking for
      Throws:
      FlightBookingSystemException - if no booking exists for the given flight
